'''赫克瑟姆'''（{{lang-en|Hexham}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|h|ɛ|k|s|əm}}）是位於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]東北部[[諾森伯蘭|諾森伯蘭]]的一個城市和民政教區。在2001年，赫克瑟姆有人口11,446人<ref>{{cite web|title=Parish Headcounts: Tynedale|url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/viewFullDataset.do?instanceSelection=03070&productId=779&$ph=60_61&datasetInstanceId=3070&startColumn=1&numberOfColumns=8&containerAreaId=790480|work=Neighbourhood Statistics|publisher=Office for National Statistics|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120528161552/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/viewFullDataset.do?instanceSelection=03070&productId=779&$ph=60_61&datasetInstanceId=3070&startColumn=1&numberOfColumns=8&containerAreaId=790480|archivedate=2012-05-28|access-date=2016-03-07}}</ref>。2011年，增加到11,829人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11120353&c=NE47+6NN&d=16&e=62&g=6453413&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&o=362&m=0&r=0&s=1435501719452&enc=1|title=Town population 2011|accessdate=28 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703193052/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11120353&c=NE47+6NN&d=16&e=62&g=6453413&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&o=362&m=0&r=0&s=1435501719452&enc=1|archivedate=2015年7月3日}}</ref>。

